## In the world of software, most everything takes longer to implement than you expect. And so it's not uncommon to accomplish less in a fixed amount of time than you hope.

### In a sentence (or list of features), define a GOOD outcome for your final project. I.e., what WILL you accomplish no matter what?

I bare minimum I plan to accomplish is the game minesweeper itself, j a normal minesweeper with no abilities that I mentioned.

### In a sentence (or list of features), define a BETTER outcome for your final project. I.e., what do you THINK you can accomplish before the final project's deadline?

A better outcome would be the minesweeper game along with some abilities implemented with at least 1 or 2 that is coded without any errors.

### In a sentence (or list of features), define a BEST outcome for your final project. I.e., what do you HOPE to accomplish before the final project's deadline?

The best outcome would be a perfectly functioning minesweeper game with three different difficulties. The harder the difficulty, the bigger the grid and with more mines like in normal minesweeper. It would also have minimum 3 unique abilities that could help the user solve the game.

## In a paragraph or more, outline your next steps. What new skills will you need to acquire? What topics will you need to research? If working with one of two classmates, who will do what?

I plan to research videos on how to code minesweeper. I want to also learn to how to implement unique images into my own code similar to the Hurricane Irma with the hurricane image. That way I can have my own images like bombs and flags that I can implement into my game.
